data.description: PRICE ADJUSTMENT!!!  How lucky are you! This beautiful house, 2 bedroom, 2 bath is move in ready. Fully updated two years ago and it still looks brand new. The owners made a few more great updates that you will truly appreciate. Brand new fenced in yard, new washer and dryer, 2021, New refrigerator 2023, microwave 2022, new shed and new garage door opener. All you need to do is unpack your bags and barbecue and start making new memories. This amazing home may be considered a 2 bedroom, however, the 3rd room with barn doors could very well be one, 11 x 15.5. The double size lot gives you a spacious backyard plenty of room to entertain or let the dogs run free. Roof 2022. Only a short distance from US 19 and 14 minutes to the Suncoast Parkway. Don't let this opportunity pass you by, this home will not last long, call today to set up an appointment.
